    "title": "Sheria za Msingi",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "sheria za msingi",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kwenye Maandiko, Mungu wa Kweli ndiye mwenye mamlaka ya juu kabisa. Sheria za Mungu zinajumuisha amri za kufanya na za kutofanya. Sheria kuu mbili zinafupisha amri za kufanya:</p><ul><li><p>“Mpende BWANA Mungu wako kwa moyo wako wote, kwa roho yako yote, na kwa nguvu zako zote” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37\">Mathayo 22:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:30\">Marko 12:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">Luka 10:27</a>).</p></li><li><p>“Mpende jirani yako kama unavyojipenda” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">Mambo ya Walawi 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:19\">Mathayo 19:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:31\">Marko 12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">Luka 10:27</a>).</p></li></ul><p>Tunaweza kuona sheria hizi mbili katika amri za kuamuru za Amri Kumi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:2-Exod20:17\">Kutoka 20:2–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:6-Deut5:21\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 5:6–21</a>):</p><ul><li><p>“Kumbuka siku ya Sabato”</p></li><li><p>“Waheshimu baba yako na mama yako”</p></li></ul><p>Amri za kukataza huweka mipaka kati ya mema na mabaya. Amri mbili za kwanza kati ya Amri Kumi ni muhimu:</p><ul><li><p>“Usiwe na miungu mingine isipokuwa Mimi” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:3\">Kutoka 20:3</a>).</p></li><li><p>“Usijitengenezee sanamu ya kuchonga ya mfano wa kitu chochote … Usivisujudie wala kuviabudu” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:4-Exod20:5\">Kutoka 20:4–5</a>).</p></li></ul><p>Vitendo hivi vilivyokatazwa vinapingana na amri ya msingi ya kumpenda Mungu.</p><p>Vitabu vya manabii vinaonyesha kwamba Mungu hutumia sheria hizi kuhukumu matendo ya Waisraeli. Mungu pia huzitumia kuhukumu mtawala yeyote, kikundi, au mtu mahali popote au wakati wowote. Wale wanaovunja sheria hizi kuu wanamkataa Mugu wa kweli, na hii husababisha hukumu ya kimungu na majanga kwa wenye dhambi.</p><p><u>Sehemu za kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:2-Exod20:17\">Kutoka 20:2–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">Mambo ya Walawi 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:6-Deut5:21\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 5:6–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:7-Jer2:13\">Yeremia 2:7–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:8-Jer3:11\">3:8–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:1-Jer5:9\">5:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:10-Jer6:21\">6:10–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:16-Jer7:29\">7:16–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:9-Jer8:13\">8:9–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:6-Jer11:14\">11:6–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:1-Jer17:4\">17:1–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:1-Jer22:9\">22:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:10-Jer23:12\">23:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer34:8-Jer34:20\">34:8–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:19\">Mathayo 19:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37\">22:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:30-Mark12:31\">Marko 12:30–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">Luka 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:13\">1 Wakorintho 13:13</a></p>",
